---
title: NYC Street Cart Steak Bowls with Roasted Veggies & Garlicky White Sauce
description: One of our all-time favorite NYC eats? A bowl packed with fluffy rice, richly-spiced meat, tender veggies, and creamy sauce. For this version, we’re sending sirloin steak that’s pre-marinated in turmeric, paprika, garlic powder, and other seasonings so you get extra-flavorful results in no time. For even more depth, we add aromatic shawarma spices, then sear the meat until tender. It’s served over rice with roasted onion, tomato, and bell pepper, plus garlicky white sauce AND hot sauce for creamy, spicy goodness in every bite.
